        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>这是一个初创博客的个人使用指导文章</p><h2 id="hexo指令"><a href="#hexo指令" class="headerlink" title="hexo指令"></a>hexo指令</h2><h3 id="hexo主页"><a href="#hexo主页" class="headerlink" title="hexo主页"></a>hexo主页</h3><p><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">hexo</a></p><h3 id="hexo三连"><a href="#hexo三连" class="headerlink" title="hexo三连"></a>hexo三连</h3><h4 id="git-bash"><a href="#git-bash" class="headerlink" title="git bash"></a>git bash</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate &amp;&amp; hexo deploy </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="vscode"><a href="#vscode" class="headerlink" title="vscode"></a>vscode</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean; hexo generate; hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="运行项目"><a href="#运行项目" class="headerlink" title="运行项目"></a>运行项目</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
